stimulus:
In this game, you will see some different monsters on the screen.

When you tap on a monster, it will give you some stars!

Every monster can give you stars, but every monster is different!
Check your knowledge before you begin!

Thanks for playing with us! You earned 87 stars!



Wow, that's a lot of stars!
Now we just a few more questions for you...
Which, if any, of these monsters ever gave you 1 star?
Which, if any, of these monsters ever gave you 2 stars?
Which, if any, of these monsters ever gave you 4 stars?
Which, if any, of these monsters ever gave you 6 stars?
Which, if any, of these monsters ever gave you 8 stars?
Which monster did you like the most?
